# oh-my-cursor

- Follow the repository root `AGENTS.md` for agent catalog, paths, and Team pipeline semantics.
- **Terminal**: use `oh-my-cursor agent <role> -- "task"` or `node scripts/run-agent.mjs ...`; Team: `oh-my-cursor team 'N:role "task"'` or `node scripts/run-team.mjs ...` (see `AGENTS.md`).
- Role prompts live in `agents/<role>.md`; only use roles that exist there.
- Team artifacts and state: `.oh-my-cursor/plans/` and `.oh-my-cursor/state/` (not `.omc/`).
- For Team behavior details in-editor, use the **team** skill under `.cursor/skills/team/SKILL.md`.
